divs: sighting detailsstanding outside my home in the woods on 8\25\2011 at about 9:30 pm. i looked up to the north west and saw a super bright star, or at least at first thought it was a star. i started watching it because i hadent seen one that bright before. it had red, blue, green, white,and gold flashing lights going around it, repeating then random flashing in different order. it had a bright white starlight center. i watched this for about 15 min, it seemed to hover in the sky and stayed in one area it was far away and the other stars look small in compairason. i see alot of odd lights in the sky.. because of where i live.. that i have thought might be unexplainable but for the first time i know i saw a ufo. with out question it was amazing. i now know for sure we are not alone. i went to get banok's. 1 min it was gone.
Summary: I live in the woods, saw a bright what I thought was a star. At closer observaction I realize it was not moving,but staying in one spot
